              <span class="review-date">Il y a 2 jours</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="review-rating">★★★★★</div>
        </div>
        <div class="review-content">
          <div class="review-title">Qualité exceptionnelle !</div>
          <div class="review-text">
            Absolument ravie de mon achat. La qualité du tissu est excellente et la coupe parfaite. Je recommande vivement !
          </div>
          <div class="review-images">
            <img src="https://i.imgur.com/placeholder1.jpg" alt="Photo client" class="review-image" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
          </div>
          <span class="verified-badge">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/>
            </svg>
            Achat vérifié
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

